wordageddon.model

Class GameSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • wordageddon.model.GameSession

  • public class GameSession
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a complete game session in Wordageddon. This class manages the entire game session including questions, answers, scoring, and session metadata. It provides methods to track progress, calculate scores, and generate detailed reports.
    Since:
    2025
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gregorio Barberio, Francesco Peluso, Davide Quaranta, Ciro Ronca
